to the chase.

15:30.790 --> 15:31.985
You clearly
have an agenda.

15:31.990 --> 15:33.651
Well, we found
a 5150 on your record.

15:33.660 --> 15:37.096
3 years ago, you broke into
your ex-boyfriend's home,

15:37.100 --> 15:38.556
And when he woke up,
you were

15:38.570 --> 15:39.765
Standing over him
holding a knife.

15:39.770 --> 15:41.761
I was wondering when
that was gonna pop up.

15:41.770 --> 15:42.896
It was
a long time ago.

15:42.900 --> 15:45.460
You were on a psychiatric hold
for 72 hours.

15:45.470 --> 15:47.962
Look. I was in a bad
place back then.

15:47.980 --> 15:50.199
