18:16.420 --> 18:18.889
But if there is
evidence to be found,

18:18.890 --> 18:21.655
We will find it, andrea.

18:30.600 --> 18:32.637
Hey, jack,
got a minute?

18:32.640 --> 18:34.699
No. Sorry.
I don't.

18:34.710 --> 18:36.439
I know about
you and amanda.

18:36.440 --> 18:38.078
What are you
talking about?

18:38.080 --> 18:39.150
What are you doing?

18:39.150 --> 18:41.403
