bracelet or a watch.

19:56.720 --> 19:59.052
Yep, but there's
no clear view until

19:59.060 --> 20:01.154
I got the video from
the parking garage.

20:01.160 --> 20:03.857
See, the car's plates
are smartly covered up,

20:03.870 --> 20:07.022
But, see,
there's the watch.

20:07.040 --> 20:10.089
