20:10.100 --> 20:13.229
It's a 1978
rolex daytona 6263.

20:13.240 --> 20:15.334
That's a $35,000
watch.

20:15.340 --> 20:16.603
How do you
know that?

20:16.610 --> 20:18.169
I dated this rich kid
in high school.

20:18.180 --> 20:19.670
He actually got one
for graduation.

20:19.680 --> 20:21.341
Why didn't you
marry him?

20:21.350 --> 20:24.615
Ben: And it's listed right here
in the divorce settlement.

20:24.620 --> 20:27.317
Kenneth brown got possession
of a daytona watch.

20:27.320 --> 20:30.517
I'll call beth.

20:35.730 --> 20:37.289
[melissa crying]

20:37.300 --> 20:39.894
Door's open.

20:43.070 --> 20:44.731
[knock knock]

20:44.740 --> 20:46.959
Melissa?

20:46.980 --> 20:50.075
[melissa sobbing]

20:50.080 --> 20:51.707
It's lieutenant davis.

20:51.710 --> 20:56.250
[sobbing continues]

20:56.250 --> 20:58.048
Where's kenneth?

20:58.050 --> 21:02.715
I don't know.
He left.

21:03.660 --> 21:06.083
Melissa, what happened?

21:06.090 --> 21:08.252
Someone e-mailed me
this video.

21:08.260 --> 21:10.251
