from an anonymous e-mail,

21:10.270 --> 21:12.523
But I know that
andrea sent it.

21:12.530 --> 21:15.022
How could I have
been so stupid?

21:15.040 --> 21:17.737
He kept telling me that
his ex-wife was crazy,

21:17.740 --> 21:21.699
