trying to scare us.

21:21.710 --> 21:24.771
This whole time,
he was sleeping with her.

21:24.780 --> 21:28.375
Melissa, do you
recognize this?

21:28.380 --> 21:31.714
It's kenneth's watch.

21:31.720 --> 21:33.848
Andrea was attacked
last night,

21:33.860 --> 21:36.852
And the man who attacked her
was wearing that watch.

21:36.860 --> 21:38.510
We need to talk to kenneth.

21:38.530 --> 21:41.659
If there is something
you're not telling us,

21:41.660 --> 21:44.891
Now is a good time.

22:01.380 --> 22:03.678
Where'd you get this?

22:03.690 --> 22:05.510
Melissa: I found it
in kenneth's trunk

22:05.520 --> 22:08.444
<i>The day after andrea's
dog was killed.</i>

22:09.360 --> 22:11.055
You were
protecting him?

22:11.060 --> 22:14.121
I didn't know what to do.
I thought I loved him.

22:14.130 --> 22:18.158
I'm scared that he might
do something stupid,

22:18.170 --> 22:19.797
He was so angry.

22:19.800 --> 22:22.462
He said that he
was gonna hurt andrea.

22:22.470 --> 22:23.869
Put an apb out on
kenneth. Call jack.

22:23.870 --> 22:27.170
Tell him to meet me
at the museum.

22:37.880 --> 22:42.215
John, I just wanted
to say thank you.

22:43.990 --> 22:48.450
Andrea: Hi. Excuse me.
I need to check on the caterer.

23:24.630 --> 23:27.270
Yeah. So lovely
meeting you.

23:27.270 --> 23:28.396
Robyn...
Yeah?

23:28.400 --> 23:33.031
I think she went to
the kitchen upstairs.

23:33.040 --> 23:35.008
Upstairs.

23:43.180 --> 23:46.184
[door closes]

23:49.660 --> 23:52.459
Robyn?

23:55.360 --> 23:56.691
Kenneth.

23:56.700 --> 23:57.690
I need to talk
to you.

23:57.700 --> 24:00.397
No. You stay away from me.
You can't be here.

24:00.400 --> 24:01.526
I just want
to talk, andrea.

24:01.540 --> 24:03.998
I have a restraining order.
Don't you get near me.

24:04.010 --> 24:05.739
Have you lost
your mind?

24:05.740 --> 24:07.162
I'm calling
the police.

24:07.180 --> 24:08.659
Why would you
send that video?

24:08.680 --> 24:10.739
Why'd you have to drag
melissa into this?

24:10.750 --> 24:12.605
You stay away
from me. Oh!

24:12.610 --> 24:14.942
Oht

24:19.990 --> 24:21.389
Beth: Stay down.

24:21.390 --> 24:23.882
[handcuffs click]

24:23.890 --> 24:25.858
You ok?

24:25.860 --> 24:28.557
Mm-hmm.

24:35.070 --> 24:37.164
Andrea: I don't know what I ever
loved about that man.

24:37.170 --> 24:39.138
Jack: You sent the
video to melissa.

24:39.140 --> 24:40.904
Why would you
do that?

24:40.910 --> 24:42.332
You knew it
would provoke him.

24:42.340 --> 24:44.729
He killed my dog.
He attacked me.

24:44.750 --> 24:47.048
I wanted melissa to see
what kind of man

24:47.050 --> 24:48.302
She was marrying.

24:48.320 --> 24:50.049
And why didn't
you tell us that

24:50.050 --> 24:51.916
You were sleeping
with kenneth?

24:51.920 --> 24:53.388
I don't get it.

24:53.390 --> 24:54.619
Because I'm not.

24:54.620 --> 24:56.679
It only happened once
two months ago.

24:56.690 --> 24:59.489
He came over to the house
to get a few of his things.

24:59.490 --> 25:00.889
We got talking.

25:00.900 --> 25:03.289
One thing led
to another, and--

25:03.300 --> 25:05.758
Man: Mrs. Brown,
we're ready for you.

25:36.300 --> 25:38.723
[camera shutter clicks]

25:38.900 --> 25:40.629
Kenneth: She seduced me.

25:40.640 --> 25:42.938
She got me to sleep
with her and filmed it.

25:42.940 --> 25:44.533
She planned
the whole thing.

25:44.540 --> 25:46.702
She is trying
to ruin my life.

25:46.710 --> 25:47.734
Beth: So you go
to the museum,

25:47.740 --> 25:48.866
Choke her out,
and try to kill her?

25:48.880 --> 25:50.177
No. I was trying
to talk to her,

25:50.180 --> 25:53.002
Your way of reasoning
is against the law, kenneth.

25:53.010 --> 25:54.148
I lost my temper,
all right?

25:54.150 --> 25:57.518
You don't get it.
She's driving me crazy.

25:57.520 --> 26:00.319
Is that why
you killed her dog?

26:00.320 --> 26:04.382
What are you--
roxy's dead?

26:04.390 --> 26:06.256
Explain this.

26:06.260 --> 26:08.649
That was found at your home.
That's canine blood.

26:08.660 --> 26:11.197
Agh, that's not
my shirt.

26:11.200 --> 26:14.420
Hang on.
There's a monogram--kb.

26:14.440 --> 26:16.534
I don't even know
where that came from.

26:16.540 --> 26:20.431
Melissa. She found it
in the trunk of your car,

26:20.440 --> 26:22.670
Turned it in to us,
and maybe you should've

26:22.680 --> 26:24.739
Taken off your rolex
when you attacked andrea

26:24.750 --> 26:26.570
Last night in
the parking garage.

26:26.580 --> 26:28.901
We have you on
surveillance, kenneth.

26:28.920 --> 26:30.046
[scoffs]

26:30.050 --> 26:34.044
I have no idea what
you're talking about.

26:34.060 --> 26:35.642
I was with clients
last night.

26:35.660 --> 26:37.287
I had a last-minute
walk-through

26:37.290 --> 26:38.689
