Of the messages left on
the walls of andrea's house.

27:14.960 --> 27:17.429
Beth: This guy has got a prior
for domestic assault.

27:17.430 --> 27:18.955
And our stalker likes
to hit women.

27:18.970 --> 27:20.267
Ben: And get this--
his very first show

27:20.270 --> 27:22.329
