with her?

27:53.030 --> 27:54.168
Is that any
of your business?

27:54.170 --> 27:55.797
Well, she's a wealthy
older woman.

27:55.800 --> 27:57.859
She funds your work.
She put on your first show.

27:57.870 --> 28:01.170
Maybe when the money
and the favors dried up,

28:01.180 --> 28:02.261
You decided
to make her pay.

28:02.280 --> 28:03.873
I don't know what
you're talking about.

28:03.880 --> 28:05.177
Really? Because I have
a video of you

28:05.180 --> 28:08.047
Assaulting her
in a parking garage.

28:08.050 --> 28:09.245
No, you don't.

28:09.250 --> 28:12.242
