a real daytona, right?

28:18.430 --> 28:22.719
Damon, you think she
gave you a $35,000 watch

28:22.730 --> 28:25.290
For a little tail?

28:25.300 --> 28:29.089
You look pretty stupid,
but no one's that dumb.

28:29.100 --> 28:30.363
You did it.

28:30.370 --> 28:32.065
You attacked andrea.

28:32.070 --> 28:34.459
Now tell me why.

28:40.680 --> 28:41.841
It doesn't add up.

28:41.850 --> 28:44.444
Kenneth had an alibi
for the attack in the garage.

28:44.450 --> 28:47.579
Even andrea admitted
he loved the dog.

28:54.830 --> 28:57.822
